sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant UI as Model Studio
  participant W as Web Worker
  participant API as API
  participant DB as PostgreSQL
  participant J as Recompute Worker
  participant S as SSE
  U->>UI: adjust weight / threshold
  UI->>W: preview(normalized facts, draft config)
  W-->>UI: scores + ranks + visibility
  UI-->>U: all loaded visuals morph
  U->>API: save & activate
  API->>DB: transaction(config version + log + outbox)
  DB-->>J: wake-up notification
  J->>DB: compute new score snapshot
  J->>DB: validate and atomically activate
  DB-->>S: snapshot activated
  S-->>UI: invalidate shared context
  UI-->>U: all modules refresh to same snapshot
